@Crypto__Chicks We're so grateful to @Crypto__Chicks (and are so happy we still hold a chick) and all the other hardworking #NFT projects that have become stepping stones to support other women-led projects. Vamos por mas!!

For a while, we knew this would be the 1st 1/1 for Sister Alchemy LLC, we just didn't have the liquidity... yet.

We sold 1 of our 2 @Crypto__Chicks - a bittersweet 10x in 3mo move - so we put a part of the earnings into this new piece, proudly supporting a #LatinaNFTartist.

As sisters, there was so much about this piece that resonated with us: the two women, the inspiring words, even the title which is emblematic of a majority of our sister talks.

As latinas in this space, it's an honor to be able to support a fellow latina artist. #WomeninNFTs
